{
  "id": "RAW_01f461",
  "title": "谷歌偷偷搞了个神秘模型 Nano-Banana？实测：强到离谱，但有 3 大硬伤 ｜ 机器之心",
  "url": "https://www.jiqizhixin.com/articles/2025-08-26-8",
  "date": "2025-08-26 07:26:47",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section>\n   <section>\n    <blockquote>\n     <p>神秘AI模型Nano-Banana火了，冒出一堆假网站，李鬼和李逵傻傻分不清。</p>\n    </blockquote>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p>最近，AI 社区又冒出一个神秘的图像生成和编辑模型，名叫 Nano-Banana。</p>\n  <p>起初它在 LMArena 平台的「Battle」模式中被发现，但未在公开排行榜上列出，也没有官方开发者明确声称其归属。</p>\n  <p>不过很多网友循着蛛丝马迹，猜测<strong>这可能是谷歌的研究模型</strong>。</p>\n  <p>上周二，谷歌 AI Studio 产品负责人 Logan Kilpatrick 在 X 上发布了一个香蕉表情符号。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_d183b1\" data-ratio=\"0.15925925925925927\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1178\" data-height=\"188\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"92\" data-imgfileid=\"503503633\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"1\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/6f887eed-2777-42ce-842d-ae47db06ba5b/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>谷歌 DeepMind 产品经理 Naina Raisinghani 也发布了一张与意大利艺术家 Maurizio Cattelan 2019 年创作的胶带粘贴香蕉艺术作品类似的图片。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231148_f58ffd\" data-ratio=\"0.9574074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1182\" data-height=\"1132\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"554\" data-imgfileid=\"503503635\" data-original-style=\"width:100%;\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/38d570e1-227f-4afe-9bcf-5ec8a6979e24/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>再加上谷歌过去曾将其较小的模型称为「Nano」，而且其生成图像的质感与 Google 的 Imagen 或 Gemini 系列相似。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_4407dd\" data-ratio=\"0.2564814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1224\" data-height=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"503503636\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/084e7718-812e-47de-b181-cf518be1379e/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"2\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>以上种种，似乎都在暗示它出自谷歌之手。</p>\n  <p>该模型不仅在<strong>文本编辑、风格融合和场景理解</strong>等方面表现更优，还可以上传两张图片、输入提示词将其中的元素融合。</p>\n  <p>比如，上传一摞书和卧室床头柜的图片，输入提示词「Flip stack of books to be upright and put on table between two bookends.」</p>\n  <p>它能精准理解复杂文本提示，将横放的三本书立起来，并加上书挡摆放到柜子上。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_f38c8e\" data-ratio=\"0.549074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1108\" data-height=\"608\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"317\" data-imgfileid=\"503503637\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"4\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/433949a6-d41e-4e96-bd52-b681bacda4e0/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"3\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>上传一张模特照再加上一张棒球帽子图，输入提示词：「Put the baseball hat on the woman.」</p>\n  <p>棒球帽上有着复杂的文字和图案刺绣，Nano-Banana 编辑后的图片保留了帽子上的所有细节，同时光线、视角和构图也能一致性。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_c8034f\" data-ratio=\"0.5555555555555556\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1108\" data-height=\"616\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"321\" data-imgfileid=\"503503639\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"5\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/eaf0b32e-e3f1-4a5e-9202-5af6a35fb5fc/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"4\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>在产品照片、场景搭建图、广告等商业场景下，Nano-Banana 的表现也稳得一批。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_8a6af1\" data-ratio=\"0.5481481481481482\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1112\" data-height=\"610\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"317\" data-imgfileid=\"503503640\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"6\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3b2fbe93-48c8-4be1-a7c9-10da2c762c41/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"5\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>当然，它也并非完美无缺，在某些情况下，Nano-Banana 生成的图像可能出现反射、光照逻辑或物体位置不一致等视觉问题，人物的手指也偶尔出现畸形的情况。</p>\n  <p>如果细看上图中生成的书籍，就会发现其中的瑕疵：书名出现了「鬼画符」。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_2d367a\" data-ratio=\"1.45\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"180\" data-width=\"180\" data-height=\"261\" data-imgfileid=\"503503641\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"7\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/23ae6ee8-51ac-4ed9-bddc-ff1d2442f9c5/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"6\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>由于尚无官方 API 或正式的官网链接，我们<strong>只能通过 LMArena 随机体验</strong>该模型。</p>\n  <p>换句话说，每次都得靠运气才能遇到 Nano Banana，体验很不稳定。</p>\n  <p>更搞笑的是，网上出现了一堆假网站，声称提供 Nano Banana 服务，让不少网友李鬼和李逵傻傻分不清。</p>\n  <p><strong>Nano-Banana 一手测评</strong></p>\n  <p>我们也来了个一手测评。</p>\n  <p>打开 lmarena 官网，选择 Battle 模式，可以直接输入提示词进行文生图，也可以上传图片、输入提示词再进行 AI 编辑。</p>\n  <p>官网链接：https://lmarena.ai/</p>\n  <p>页面会出现两个匿名模型同时生成图片，只有当我们选出其中生成质量最好的一张图片时，平台才会亮出对战双方的身份。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_0dd273\" data-ratio=\"0.5944444444444444\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2320\" data-height=\"1380\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"344\" data-imgfileid=\"503503642\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"8\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/be930a98-9841-469d-a374-3debff8cca3b/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"7\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>先来试试<strong>文生图</strong>效果。</p>\n  <p>我们输入同样的提示词：Present a portrait-style image in a Polaroid photo shoot style. In the picture, there is a makeup artist with long, loose curly hair, wearing oversized clothing. She has a delicate face and exudes a casual vibe, posing with a peace sign directly at the camera, creating an ultra-free atmosphere. The image has a slight grainy texture, with vibrant and captivating colors，1:1.</p>\n  <p>第一幅是 Nano Banana 的「作品」，第二幅是 ChatGPT 生成的效果。前者生成的图片背景中有杂乱的眼影盘、指甲油等，更符合提示词中的「化妆师」身份，而且人物的动作、服装细节更自然，手部也没有明显的瑕疵；而后者背景较为单一，大拇指也有些虚化。</p>\n  <section data-id=\"91330\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\">\n   <section>\n    <section data-role=\"animate\" data-width=\"100%\">\n     <section data-divisor=\"1\" data-width=\"200%\">\n      <section data-width=\"50%\">\n       <section>\n        <section data-width=\"100%\">\n         <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n          <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;93ca03e1-8ed5-472f-b3fe-2cc397977f8a&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:398,&quot;width&quot;:398,&quot;currHeight&quot;:398,&quot;currWidth&quot;:398,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1024,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1024,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.712890625,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FRjBzbOFUAonE8ixef2qcuX2MnBd%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;RjBzbOFUAonE8ixef2qcuX2MnBd&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:2374361,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n           <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_eb711a\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" data-width=\"1024\" data-height=\"1024\" data-imgfileid=\"503503645\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align: baseline;width: 100%;\" data-index=\"9\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/2539b4cd-0724-4f0c-a850-c36aa333558c/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"8\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"50%\">\n       <section>\n        <section data-width=\"100%\">\n         <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n          <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;091a6f83-08ca-4d9c-a00a-0fb0847e6fed&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:398,&quot;width&quot;:398,&quot;currHeight&quot;:398,&quot;currWidth&quot;:398,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1024,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1024,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.712890625,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FGjYlbo0WIovVLRxuynkcXWOIn9g%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;GjYlbo0WIovVLRxuynkcXWOIn9g&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:1402842,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n           <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_526931\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" data-width=\"1024\" data-height=\"1024\" data-imgfileid=\"503503644\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align: baseline;width: 100%;\" data-index=\"10\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/aecdd414-592f-4576-96a2-cbba5eea0c71/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"9\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p>再来试试它的<strong>图片编辑</strong>功能。</p>\n  <p>上传一张旧金山阿拉莫广场的野餐照片，输入提示词：Add some humanoid robots in the park，make them blend with the environment.</p>\n  <p>乍一看我们还以为 Nano Banana「罢工」了，直到在画面右侧找到了一个正在走路的类人机器人，它完全融入环境，毫无违和感。</p>\n  <section data-id=\"91330\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\">\n   <section>\n    <section data-role=\"animate\" data-width=\"100%\">\n     <section data-divisor=\"1\" data-width=\"200%\">\n      <section data-width=\"50%\">\n       <section>\n        <section data-width=\"100%\">\n         <section>\n          <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n           <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;93ca03e1-8ed5-472f-b3fe-2cc397977f8a&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:398,&quot;width&quot;:398,&quot;currHeight&quot;:398,&quot;currWidth&quot;:398,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1024,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1024,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.712890625,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FRjBzbOFUAonE8ixef2qcuX2MnBd%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;RjBzbOFUAonE8ixef2qcuX2MnBd&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:2374361,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n            <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n             <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;26addf95-8cb1-402a-93a6-ed3a3e0933bb&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:771,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;currHeight&quot;:771,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1024,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:771,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1024,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FGAribgT5JoXEylxLBz7cSSvknXf%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;GAribgT5JoXEylxLBz7cSSvknXf&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:229238,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n              <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_267674\" data-ratio=\"0.7529296875\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" data-width=\"1024\" data-height=\"771\" data-imgfileid=\"503503646\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\" data-index=\"11\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/57472ca2-28a0-4f83-987e-33c6dae4629d/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"10\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n             </section>\n            </section>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"50%\">\n       <section>\n        <section data-width=\"100%\">\n         <section>\n          <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n           <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;091a6f83-08ca-4d9c-a00a-0fb0847e6fed&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:398,&quot;width&quot;:398,&quot;currHeight&quot;:398,&quot;currWidth&quot;:398,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1024,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1024,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.712890625,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FGjYlbo0WIovVLRxuynkcXWOIn9g%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;GjYlbo0WIovVLRxuynkcXWOIn9g&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:1402842,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n            <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n             <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;c0d8846f-6436-4c31-9084-6cbb1a405e84&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1276,&quot;width&quot;:1756,&quot;currHeight&quot;:1276,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1756,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1276,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1756,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FSVorbsFQho3aZdxf1JqcaNNqngd%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;SVorbsFQho3aZdxf1JqcaNNqngd&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:3730389,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n              <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_32d9c8\" data-ratio=\"0.7268518518518519\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1756\" data-height=\"1276\" data-imgfileid=\"503503647\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\" data-index=\"12\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/85970864-2880-4ba6-b902-3f011aeab7ce/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"22\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n             </section>\n            </section>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p>我们上传一张人物摄影照片，让 Nano Banana 进行逆向工程描绘其创作过程。</p>\n  <p>提示词：Show the set being set up before, the model is sitting up scrolling her phone, there is a woman behind the model fixing her hair, a man up on a ladder, hanging the curtain in the background, revealing the studio behind it.</p>\n  <section data-id=\"91330\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\">\n   <section>\n    <section data-role=\"animate\" data-width=\"100%\">\n     <section data-divisor=\"1\" data-width=\"200%\">\n      <section data-width=\"50%\">\n       <section>\n        <section data-width=\"100%\">\n         <section>\n          <section>\n           <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n            <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;93ca03e1-8ed5-472f-b3fe-2cc397977f8a&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:398,&quot;width&quot;:398,&quot;currHeight&quot;:398,&quot;currWidth&quot;:398,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1024,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1024,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.712890625,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FRjBzbOFUAonE8ixef2qcuX2MnBd%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;RjBzbOFUAonE8ixef2qcuX2MnBd&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:2374361,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n             <section>\n              <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n               <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;26addf95-8cb1-402a-93a6-ed3a3e0933bb&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:771,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;currHeight&quot;:771,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1024,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:771,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1024,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FGAribgT5JoXEylxLBz7cSSvknXf%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;GAribgT5JoXEylxLBz7cSSvknXf&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:229238,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n                <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n                 <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;cb2ba814-567e-4318-b772-f6f7e74d620e&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:456.8202080237741,&quot;width&quot;:488,&quot;currHeight&quot;:456.8202080237741,&quot;currWidth&quot;:488,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1260,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1346,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.362555720653789,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FSc82bKn8LoBpsuxkuauc9KJDnLb%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;Sc82bKn8LoBpsuxkuauc9KJDnLb&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:2190817,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n                  <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_d9bd7f\" data-ratio=\"0.9361111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1346\" data-height=\"1260\" data-imgfileid=\"503503649\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\" data-index=\"13\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/7ebc3f44-26e4-429f-8420-ec6137046659/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"11\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n                 </section>\n                </section>\n               </section>\n              </section>\n             </section>\n            </section>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section data-width=\"50%\">\n       <section>\n        <section data-width=\"100%\">\n         <section>\n          <section>\n           <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n            <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;091a6f83-08ca-4d9c-a00a-0fb0847e6fed&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:398,&quot;width&quot;:398,&quot;currHeight&quot;:398,&quot;currWidth&quot;:398,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1024,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1024,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.712890625,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FGjYlbo0WIovVLRxuynkcXWOIn9g%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;GjYlbo0WIovVLRxuynkcXWOIn9g&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:1402842,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n             <section>\n              <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n               <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;c0d8846f-6436-4c31-9084-6cbb1a405e84&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1276,&quot;width&quot;:1756,&quot;currHeight&quot;:1276,&quot;currWidth&quot;:1756,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:1276,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1756,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:1,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FSVorbsFQho3aZdxf1JqcaNNqngd%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;SVorbsFQho3aZdxf1JqcaNNqngd&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:3730389,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n                <section data-docx-has-block-data=\"true\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-page-id=\"H6OMdD9CEoyfl1xzeVucCX1enbe\">\n                 <section data-ace-gallery-json=\"{&quot;items&quot;:[{&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;cd34e678-3a1d-4358-aee9-cd3c472c074b&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:467.81818181818187,&quot;width&quot;:498,&quot;currHeight&quot;:467.81818181818187,&quot;currWidth&quot;:498,&quot;natrualHeight&quot;:992,&quot;natrualWidth&quot;:1056,&quot;pluginName&quot;:&quot;imageUpload&quot;,&quot;scale&quot;:0.4715909090909091,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https%3A%2F%2Finternal-api-drive-stream.feishu.cn%2Fspace%2Fapi%2Fbox%2Fstream%2Fdownload%2Fpreview%2FD5o3bvtDZogPoyxRJGdc2FA6nqf%2F%3Fpreview_type%3D16&quot;,&quot;file_token&quot;:&quot;D5o3bvtDZogPoyxRJGdc2FA6nqf&quot;,&quot;image_type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:1564794,&quot;comments&quot;:[]}]}\" data-type=\"image\">\n                  <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231148_8853c5\" data-ratio=\"0.9393939393939394\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1056\" data-width=\"1056\" data-height=\"992\" data-imgfileid=\"503503651\" data-original-style=\"vertical-align: baseline;\" data-index=\"14\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/67e91e08-ebd9-4624-8137-421acf8e18c1/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"12\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n                 </section>\n                </section>\n               </section>\n              </section>\n             </section>\n            </section>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p>有网友用 Nano Banana 让碧梨和迈克尔・杰克逊跨时空自拍：</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_4fd9e3\" data-ratio=\"0.8675925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1091\" data-height=\"947\" data-imgfileid=\"503503652\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"15\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/60613469-a67c-4bf2-b511-3161487a39f2/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"13\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>我们也尝试了下。上传马斯克和奥特曼的照片，输入提示词：The two people are happily taking a selfie.</p>\n  <p>Nano Banana 确实生成了一张自拍照，马斯克的形象、动作也几乎找不出什么问题，只是奥特曼大变样。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231148_18bcf6\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2320\" data-height=\"1294\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"322\" data-imgfileid=\"503503653\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"16\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/69f5b76e-e6d2-4674-b334-41c27d2897f8/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"14\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>为了不「冤枉」它，我们又给了它一次机会，Nano Banana 还是翻车。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_836a64\" data-ratio=\"0.5592592592592592\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2312\" data-height=\"1292\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"323\" data-imgfileid=\"503503654\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"17\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/96dc6e91-3290-43df-abd8-0632fa2a53a8/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"15\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>难度继续升级。上传小扎、马斯克肖像照和一张风景照，让 Nano Banana 把两个人自然地放在图三中。</p>\n  <p>Gemini 2.0 flash 生成的效果完全认不出这两个大名人，而 Nano Banana 将二人完美融入图三环境中，不过手指等细节方面还是有瑕疵。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_469482\" data-ratio=\"0.5601851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2326\" data-height=\"1304\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"324\" data-imgfileid=\"503503655\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"18\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/584e0333-b481-410d-a1b2-475295e74a1e/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"16\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p><strong>进阶玩法</strong></p>\n  <p>如果把 Nano-Banana 和谷歌的 Veo3 结合在一起，会碰撞出怎样的火花？</p>\n  <p>@a16z 合伙人 Justine Moore 就搞了个新工作流，用于制作较长的视频。</p>\n  <p>下面这个视频是一个游戏或电影中的潜行任务场景，角色从昏暗的博物馆中盗取一幅名画，触发了激光警报。<a href=\"https://www.jiqizhixin.com/admin/articles/new\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/91965cb8-afbf-4c43-87f8-db631f9dbb81/1756192905482.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a></p>\n  <p>她还放出了制作教程。提取第一个视频片段的最后一帧，将该帧上传到 lmarena 上的 Nano Banana，提示生成下一个场景，例如「角色转向走廊」，然后将新生成的帧用 Veo 3 进行动画制作。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_2f9379\" data-ratio=\"0.39537037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1178\" data-height=\"466\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"229\" data-imgfileid=\"503503677\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"19\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/40dd9ca2-9ac4-4b6f-aea3-a6546d76ddbc/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"17\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>X 网友 @ZHO_ZHO_ZHO 则发现了 Nano-Banana 另一种好玩的用法 —— 把插画变成手办。</p>\n  <p>上传一张图片，输入提示词：turn this photo into a character figure. Behind it, place a box with the character’s image printed on it, and a computer showing the Blender modeling process on its screen. In front of the box, add a round plastic base with the character figure standing on it. Make the PVC material look clear, and set the scene indoors if possible.</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231149_7cc10d\" data-ratio=\"1.3421828908554572\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1017\" data-width=\"1017\" data-height=\"1365\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"776\" data-imgfileid=\"503503678\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"20\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/be2c5476-d214-4633-8b3b-b8e13ad1d9a7/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"18\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>据该博主测评，Nano-Banana 生成的图几乎没有 AI 味，五官和细节都保留得很好，真实感十足。</p>\n  <p>然后再用 Veo3 将其制作为 8 秒视频。提示词：Pick up the figure with both hands and show it from all angles.<a href=\"https://www.jiqizhixin.com/admin/articles/new\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/acd8dc59-e657-4a49-91c2-baa5c92b2def/1756192933358.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a></p>\n  <p>底下评论区不少网友也按照上述工作流整活。比如哪吒双手抱拳的：<a href=\"https://www.jiqizhixin.com/admin/articles/new\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/fd3b86e0-33ea-4bc9-9df3-a20d0b453be2/1756192946016.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a></p>\n  <p>还有哆啦 A 梦的，正面看哆啦 A 梦的尾巴挺正常，但转个身就大变样：<a href=\"https://www.jiqizhixin.com/admin/articles/new\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/e78afa14-19ca-4ad7-9f2c-962e2353aafc/1756192961332.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a></p>\n  <p>我们也复刻了下，上传一张 Q 版插画图片，输入以上提示词。</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231148_402856\" data-ratio=\"0.4777777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1410\" data-height=\"674\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"276\" data-imgfileid=\"503503679\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"21\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/5e917735-56cc-4de6-b4e7-a8e3e3215369/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"19\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>效果如下：</p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250826231148_2f7488\" data-ratio=\"0.40925925925925927\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2348\" data-height=\"960\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"236\" data-imgfileid=\"503503681\" data-original-style=\"width:100%;\" data-index=\"22\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/99911c93-cb28-4c21-83c5-cd5e8d639863/640.png\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"20\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>最后打开 Gemini 2.5 Pro，选择 Video，上传生成的图片，输入提示词，静待 1 分钟左右，就能得到一段 8 秒视频。<a href=\"https://www.jiqizhixin.com/admin/articles/new\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/419801c5-335a-4a35-a5ee-26ad4555e658/1756192983011.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a></p>\n  <p>上周末，谷歌 Veo 3 对所有 Gemini 用户免费开放，供其体验 AI 视频生成功能。</p>\n  <p>不过，这项免费体验活动只持续到太平洋时间 8 月 24 日晚上 10 点（北京时间 8 月 25 日上午 1 点） 。在此期间，免费用户每天最多可以生成 3 个 8 秒的视频片段，每个视频都包含自动生成的音频。</p>\n  <p>通常，Veo 3 的视频生成功能仅对 Google AI Pro 或 Ultra 订阅用户开放。Pro 用户每天可生成 3 个视频，而 Ultra 用户的配额为 10 个视频。</p>\n  <p>感兴趣的朋友也去体验一波吧。</p>\n  <p><sup>https://x.com/ginacostag_/status/1959234207127134340</sup></p>\n  <p><sup>https://x.com/venturetwins/status/1957155767888548160</sup></p>\n  <p><sup>https://x.com/techhalla/status/1959186906115354692</sup></p>\n  <p><sup>https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1958550998815023573</sup></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌神秘图像生成与编辑模型 Nano-Banana 实测表现出色，但在可用性和细节处理上存在明显缺陷。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌神秘图像生成与编辑模型 Nano-Banana 实测表现出色，但在可用性和细节处理上存在明显缺陷。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了神秘 AI 图像生成与编辑模型 Nano-Banana，该模型在 LMArena 平台被发现，诸多线索表明其可能出自谷歌。Nano-Banana 在文本编辑、风格融合、场景理解及多图元素融合方面表现卓越，尤其在商业场景下生成图像质量高，细节保留完整。文章通过实测对比，展示了其在文生图和图编辑上的强大能力，例如精确理解复杂提示词、将元素融入环境。然而，模型存在三大硬伤：反射/光照逻辑不一致、人物手指畸形、生成文字“鬼画符”。更严重的是，目前仅能通过 LMArena 随机体验，缺乏官方 API 和稳定服务，且网上充斥大量假冒网站，严重影响了用户获取真实信息和安全体验的途径。文章还介绍了 Nano-Banana 与谷歌 Veo 3 结合生成长视频和手办动画的进阶玩法。",
  "mainPoints": [
